title: Markets cheer Credit Suisse - but no lift for Lloyds
text:
Markets cheer Credit Suisse - but no lift for Lloyds Wednesday, April 25, 2018 - 01:35
Credit Suisse reports a 16.4 percent year-on-year rise in first-quarter net income and profits at Lloyds Bank jump by 23 percent. David Pollard looks at whether the bad times are finally over for banks.
